<li>I was so saddened to hear about the loss of your mother.  May her memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time. Your mother will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt condolences.  May you find peace and comfort in the days ahead.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, I offer my condolences on the passing of your beloved mother.</li>
<li>Your mother was a remarkable woman, and I will always cherish the memories I have of her.</li>
<li>Sending love and prayers to you and your family during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss.  May your memories of your mother bring you comfort.</li>
<li>I extend my deepest sympathy and support to you and your family.</li>
<li>Please know that my thoughts and prayers are with you.</li>
<li>May God grant you and your family strength and comfort during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Your mother's warmth and kindness will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>I am truly sorry for the loss of your mother.  Her legacy will live on.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my heart during this time of grief.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sorrow I feel upon hearing of your mother's passing.</li>
    

